{"tid":554208,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人來港打疫苗成風 投訴延誤個案狂飆97倍","createTime":"2018-02-08T09:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T11:34:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"72fd068702f9a0e903910fe70070ef1bf43991c0","tid":554208,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180208/large/1518082534_4ee6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180208%2Flarge%2F1518082534_4ee6.jpg&h=f7e65879&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消委會公佈去年投訴數字，當中旅客投訴持續上升，去年接獲2,681宗，按年升30%。主席黄玉山指，其中內地訪客投訴大幅上升34%，逾2,100宗，佔整體78%，涉款2,900萬元，金額較前年增67%。內地客有關疫苗的投訴，2015年及2016年均只有4宗，但去年狂飆至392宗，大幅上升97倍，消委會總幹事黃鳳儀指，反映內地人來港注射疫苗大幅上升。<br />\n<br />\n黄玉山表示，涉及疫苗的投訴，有很多是內地人透過中介付款，來港注射子宮頸癌疫苗，但最終因疫苗短缺，未能按時注射。最近香港爆發流感，黃鳳儀留意到不少內地人也來港注射流感疫苗，她指由於香港是自由市場，價格收費完成完全視乎供求情況，但生產及供應商需留意市場供應情況及內地人來港注射疫苗趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n消委會稱留意到近期流感疫苖亦出現短缺情況，會繼續密切監察疫苗注射的投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180208/57808403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180208%2F57808403&d=dgvwQtRVwxUBrRXODtoMvfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=9b348601\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180208%2F57808403&h=d1bb328d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180208/57808403</a>"},{"pid":"0a4045e628d6cb20fbe22ef88f60f266e5c129f6","tid":554208,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:53:19.000Z","msg":"鄰國人有幾個臭錢就投訴，咁撚把炮咪黎打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74916fc66ce0dd654a957289cf17fc9d6d09969","tid":554208,"uid":68746,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T09:55:55.000Z","msg":"乜撚都搶<br />